Class KeyToGroupMap

java.lang.Object
org.jfree.data.KeyToGroupMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable
public class KeyToGroupMap
extends Object
implements Cloneable, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable, Serializable
